cu.explanation_en: Setting the GNB IPv4 address for NG-AMF to an invalid format with octet >255 will cause IP parsing errors and prevent AMF connection establishment.

du.explanation_en: Setting the absolute SSB frequency to 0 causes frequency misalignment, leading to cell search failures and synchronization issues.
du.explanation_zh: 將 SSB 絕對頻率設定為 0 會導致頻率錯位，造成小區搜索失敗和同步問題。
